                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On January 12, 1952 the First Committee began consideration of agenda item 67,
                    “the old Soviet item”; see Doc. A/1944, November 8, page 477. This matter had
                    been displaced in the legislative process by “the new Soviet item”, which the
                    Soviet Union had submitted on November 22, 1951 and on which the General
                    Assembly had completed final action on January 11, 1952 (agenda item 69). The
                    documents that <pb facs="0510" n="488" xml:id="pg_488"/> follow reconstruct the
                    chronological development of the United States Delegation involvement with
                    agenda item 67.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
